美国墨西哥乐队 Fuerza Regida 租下整间酒店以庇护洛杉矶山火的受害者https://www.nme.com/news/music/american-mexican-fuerza-regida-rent-entire-hotel-shelter-victims-wildfires-3828174?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=american-mexican-fuerza-regida-出租整间酒店避难所野火受害者Max PilleySun, 12 Jan 2025 10:35:17 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3828174 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fuerza_regida_fires.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fuerza_regida_fires.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fuerza_regida_fires-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fuerza_regida_fires-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fuerza_regida_fires-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fuerza_regida_fires-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fuerza_regida_fires-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>此举将在未来六天内保护 50 个受影响的家庭</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/american-mexican-fuerza-regida-rent-entire-hotel-shelter-victims-wildfires-3828174">美国-墨西哥乐队 Fuerza Regida 租下了整个酒店来庇护洛杉矶野火的受害者，该乐队</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fuerza_regida_fires.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fuerza_regida_fires.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fuerza_regida_fires-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fuerza_regida_fires-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fuerza_regida_fires-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fuerza_regida_fires-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fuerza_regida_fires-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>墨西哥裔美国乐队 Fuerza Regida 租下了洛杉矶的一整栋酒店，为猖獗的山火的受害者提供庇护。</p><p>这场毁灭性的火灾于 1 月 7 日爆发，迄今已造成 16 人死亡，近 18 万居民撤离家园，超过 13,400 座建筑物受损。</p><p>从周六（1 月 11 日）开始，一些逃离家园的人将能够在 Fuerza Regida 租用的一家酒店避难，为期六天。</p><p>乐队在一份声明中写道：“致我们深爱的受洛杉矶大火影响的社区：在这个充满挑战的时刻，我们为你们服务。” “我们已经出租了一家酒店，可容纳 50 多个家庭，还将为需要庇护的人提供更多空间。请注意，我们与您站在一起，并将在这个困难时期继续提供支持。房间将于太平洋时间 24 年 1 月 11 日下午 3 点提供。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DErH8srxQQf/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556